data_dc <- read.delim(file='//10.8.8.51/lv0/Move to Box/Mithun/projects/7. DS_New Training/1. data/GP_Cust_Pre_post_all_txn.txt',
                      sep = '|',header = F, col.names = c('customer_key','flag_employee','post_discount_amt','post_gross_sales_amt','post_item_qty','post_num_order','post_num_txn','pre_discount_amt','pre_gross_sales_amt','pre_item_qty','pre_num_order','pre_num_txn','addr_zip_code','ctry_cd','addr_city','addr_state_prov_code' ))

data_dc$pre_discount_rate <- abs(data_dc$pre_discount_amt)/data_dc$pre_gross_sales_amt
data_dc$post_discount_rate <- abs(data_dc$post_discount_amt)/data_dc$post_gross_sales_amt

Pre Discount Visualization by State

a5<-ggplot(pre_disc_rate_state2, aes(map_id = state)) +
  geom_map(aes(fill = median_disc), map = states_map, color ="black") +
  expand_limits(x = states_map$long, y = states_map$lat) +
  theme(legend.position = "bottom",
        axis.ticks = element_blank(),

  scale_fill_gradient(low="green", high="red") +
  guides(fill = guide_colorbar(barwidth = 10, barheight = .5)) +ggtitle("Pre Discount Rate Sate Wise")
